## üöÄ Exemplos de C√≥digo Aceito

### ‚úÖ Video Processing
```python
def extract_audio(video_path: str) -> str:
    """Extrai √°udio do v√≠deo em WAV"""
    video = VideoFileClip(video_path)
    audio_path = video_path.replace('.mp4', '_audio.wav')
    video.audio.write_audiofile(audio_path, verbose=False)
    return audio_path
```

### ‚úÖ API Endpoint
```python
@app.route('/api/browse', methods=['POST'])
def browse_files():
    try:
        path = Path(request.json.get('path', str(Path.home()))).resolve()
        if not path.exists():
            path = Path.home()
        
        items = [
            {
                'name': item.name,
                'path': str(item.resolve()),
                'type': 'dir' if item.is_dir() else 'file'
            }
            for item in path.iterdir()
        ]
        return jsonify({'items': items, 'current': str(path)})
    except Exception as e:
        return jsonify({'error': str(e)}), 400
```

### ‚úÖ Logging Essencial
```python
def process():
    add_log("1Ô∏è‚É£ Extraindo √°udio...")
    audio = extract_audio(video)
    
    add_log("2Ô∏è‚É£ Transcrevendo...")
    text = transcribe(audio)
    
    add_log("‚úÖ Conclu√≠do!")
```

